React Developer Tools - Chrome Extension

в—Џ Chrome Developer Tools extension for React
в—Џ Goal: Inspect React Component Hierarchies
в—Џ Components tab shows:
  в–  Root React components
  в–  Sub components that were rendered
в—Џ For each component, you can see and edit
  в–  props
  в–  state
в—Џ Useful for:
  в–  Understanding and Learning React
  в–  Debugging problems


